annotations.title: How to make a Banana Old Fashioned - Toronto cocktail variation

textContent:
2 oz Bourbon
0.5 oz Banana liqueur
0.25 oz Fernet Branca
2 Dashes Angostura bitters
Lemon peel

Stir and pour into rocks glass over ice
Garnish with lemon peel
